#. [side]: type=Lich, id=Mal Tera
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/04_Vale_of_Tears.cfg:76
#: data/campaigns/The_South_Guard/scenarios/05_Choice_In_The_Fog.cfg:93
